Oh! It's a pity that the same error occurred.

I have built the 'libtflite.so' by using bazel and tried to link it by using :
'g++ --std=c++11 -I/usr/local/include/tf -I/usr/include/flatbuffers/include -L/home/yd/workspace/tensorflow/bazel-bin/tensorflow/contrib/lite -ltflite demo.cpp -o demo'.
But it does not work. The errors also are:

demo.cpp:(.text+0x52): undefined reference to tflite::DefaultErrorReporter()' demo.cpp:(.text+0x79): undefined reference to tflite::FlatBufferModel::BuildFromFile(char const*, tflite::ErrorReporter*)'
demo.cpp:(.text+0x88): undefined reference to tflite::ops::builtin::BuiltinOpResolver::BuiltinOpResolver()' demo.cpp:(.text+0xbe): undefined reference to tflite::InterpreterBuilder::InterpreterBuilder(tflite::FlatBufferModel const&, tflite::OpResolver const&)'
demo.cpp:(.text+0xd7): undefined reference to tflite::InterpreterBuilder::operator()(std::unique_ptr<tflite::Interpreter, std::default_delete<tflite::Interpreter> >*)' demo.cpp:(.text+0xfd): undefined reference to tflite::Interpreter::AllocateTensors()'
demo.cpp:(.text+0x137): undefined reference to `tflite::Interpreter::Invoke()'

body:
# Oh! It's a pity that the same error occurred.
 I have built the 'libtflite.so' by using bazel and tried to link it by using :
'g++ --std=c++11 -I/usr/local/include/tf -I/usr/include/flatbuffers/include -L/home/yd/workspace/tensorflow/bazel-bin/tensorflow/contrib/lite -ltflite demo.cpp -o demo'.
But it does not work. The errors also are:

demo.cpp:(.text+0x52): undefined reference to `tflite::DefaultErrorReporter()'
demo.cpp:(.text+0x79): undefined reference to `tflite::FlatBufferModel::BuildFromFile(char const*, tflite::ErrorReporter*)'
demo.cpp:(.text+0x88): undefined reference to `tflite::ops::builtin::BuiltinOpResolver::BuiltinOpResolver()'
demo.cpp:(.text+0xbe): undefined reference to `tflite::InterpreterBuilder::InterpreterBuilder(tflite::FlatBufferModel const&, tflite::OpResolver const&)'
demo.cpp:(.text+0xd7): undefined reference to `tflite::InterpreterBuilder::operator()(std::unique_ptr<tflite::Interpreter, std::default_delete<tflite::Interpreter> >*)'
demo.cpp:(.text+0xfd): undefined reference to `tflite::Interpreter::AllocateTensors()'
demo.cpp:(.text+0x137): undefined reference to `tflite::Interpreter::Invoke()'
